data.description: Introducing this wonderful three bedroom, two bathroom ranch in Windward subdivision! As you enter the home, you are welcomed by beautiful hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings, and a fireplace to keep you cozy on those cool Georgia days and nights. The beautiful dining room is open to the living room, and youall love the large kitchen equipped with plenty of cabinets, a breakfast area, a bar with seating, and a pantry. This kitchen is sure to entice those who love to entertain, cook, and gather with friends and family during the process. Down the hallway, youall find the laundry closet,  three bedrooms, pull down attic stairs, and a full bathroom. The hardwood floors extend into the primary bedroom and combine with the vaulted ceilings to create an absolutely gorgeous space. The primary bathroom has a large garden tub, two vanity areas and a step-in shower. The huge backyard is sure to excite kids of all ages with its above ground pool surrounded by a deck and privacy wall for relaxing on lounge chairs and soaking up the sun. This home sits on 3/4 acres, and itas just waiting to be scooped up by itas new owners! Schedule your viewing today!
